- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper mentions data-driven models, but the focus is on the Koopman Operator Theory rather than traditional machine learning methods.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper discusses control design using a data-driven approach, but again, the focus is on the Koopman Operator Theory rather than traditional AI methods.
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is less likely as the paper does not focus on software development, but rather on the modeling and control of soft robots.
